{"talk":{"id":50576,"name":"Marcus Bullock: An app that helps incarcerated people stay connected to their families","description":"Over his eight-year prison sentence, Marcus Bullock was sustained by his mother's love -- and by the daily letters and photos she sent of life on the outside. Years later, as an entrepreneur, Bullock asked himself: How can I make it easier for all families to stay connected during incarceration? Enter FlikShop: an app he developed that lets families send quick postcards to loved ones in prison and help keep open a critical line of support.","slug":"marcus_bullock_an_app_that_helps_incarcerated_people_stay_connected_to_their_families","recorded_at":"2019-06-27 00:00:00","published_at":"2019-10-15 16:47:16","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:30:56","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":602,"name":"TED Salon The Macallan"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b3d47ac35690ca8a0ee8839dc4e632f244ea1a9d_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b3d47ac35690ca8a0ee8839dc4e632f244ea1a9d_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b3d47ac35690ca8a0ee8839dc4e632f244ea1a9d_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/b3d47ac35690ca8a0ee8839dc4e632f244ea1a9d_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/1f89c1793a401937f83e2bdf8f0408ff7e887ec9_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MarcusBullock_2019S-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":7457771,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MarcusBullock_2019S-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":20675182,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/MarcusBullock_2019S-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe